name: Eco Bags
overview: Incepted in 2010, Eco Bags is a partnership firm, engaged in manufacturing, supplying and exporting am environment friendly range of D Cut Bags, U Cut Bags, W Cut Bags, Shopping Bags, Carry Bags, Non Woven Plain Bags, Non Woven Printed Bags, Non Woven Pouch Bags, Non Woven Fabric Rolls and Non Woven Pillow Covers. These products are widely acknowledged among the clients for its optimum quality, neat stitching and durable finishing. Our entire product range is thoroughly tested before the final delivery at our clients’ premises is made, thereby rendering maximum client satisfaction. Offered product range is available in different colors and designs and are available with customized solutions. Our entire business operations are headed by our mentor Mr. A. Sakthivel & Mr. S.T. Subramaniam (Partners) who possess in-depth industrial experience. They are well-versed with latest market trends and their excellent leadership quality assists us in carving a distinguished position in the competitive market.
